social call during wartime.

01:44.110 --> 01:48.270
Well, it's, um… it's my grandson.

01:48.280 --> 01:49.280
Is he going over?

01:49.320 --> 01:51.540
Oh, God, no. I'd send
him to Canada first.

01:51.580 --> 01:54.590
No, he's, um…

01:54.600 --> 01:56.900
