02:04.220 --> 02:08.114
I'm afraid I… I didn't set a
very good example for the boy.

02:08.330 --> 02:10.419
Oh, you— you've
killed people.

02:10.430 --> 02:11.930
Well, even so.

02:11.940 --> 02:13.260
